resources.string: I\'m a rising junior at Georgetown University majoring in computer science and history with a minor in psychology. I spent my last summer balancing a customer service job with six computer science courses, building Android applications, and designing my own website. I\'ve tested multiple apps for Google and have extensive experience with teamwork, public speaking, and research, as I\'ve been a member of the debate team for six years. I am fluent in Java, Python, C++, XML, HTML, and CSS. I\'m looking for software engineering internships, preferably in the Bay Area.
